OL,5, A painting by the abstract Dutch artist
OL,6, Piet Mondrian has been hanging upside  
OL,7, down in various galleries for 75 years,
OL,8, an art historian has said.             
OL,10,FDespite the recent discovery, the work,
OL,11,Fentitled New York City I, will continue
OL,12,Fto be displayed the wrong way up to    
OL,13,Favoid it being damaged.                
OL,15,FThe 1941 picture was first put on      
OL,16,Fdisplay at New York's MoMA in 1945.    
OL,18,FIt has hung at the art collection of   
OL,19,Fthe German state of North              
OL,20,FRhine-Westphalia in Dusseldorf since   
OL,21,F1980.                                  
